    <outline text="Torstein Træen — Concussion and multiple fractured ribs sustained in a crash on the descent of the Col du Tourmalet during stage 6 (2026-07-09)" type="link" url="https://www.cyclingnews.com/pro-cycling/teams-riders/not-the-ending-we-wanted-for-this-yellow-adventure-torstein-traeen-out-of-tour-de-france-due-to-injuries-from-tourmalet-crash/" description="Uno-X Mobility loses the rider who had been wearing the race's yellow jersey after stage 5; Tadej Pogačar reclaimed the overall race lead the same day"/>
