    <outline text="Amadou Onana — Torn anterior cruciate ligament (ACL), sustained in the 21st minute of Belgium's Round of 16 win over the United States after a challenge with Christian Pulisic (2026-07-07)" type="link" url="https://www.espn.com/soccer/story/_/id/49298508/belgium-amadou-onana-world-cup-suffering-acl-injury" description="Belgium loses a key defensive midfielder ahead of their World Cup quarterfinal vs. Spain, and Aston Villa will be without him for a significant part of the 2026-27 season"/>
